        <div id="unit90-header" class="accordion_headings">
         &gt; 3-401 Bomb Threat or Suspicious Package
        </div> 
        <div id="unit90-content">
         <!--DIV which show/hide on click of header--> 
         <div class="accordion_child"> 
          <p><br> POLICY STATEMENT:<br> UCF is committed to providing and maintaining a safe campus environment for faculty, staff, students, and the community. Members of the university community are expected to report suspicious activities immediately to the UCF Police Department (911), and must understand and follow basic emergency procedures when confronted with suspicious substances or packages, such as Improvised Explosive Devices (IED), or bomb threats. All personnel must be familiar with the UCF Bomb Threat Plan and the UCF Building Evacuation Policy and Procedure. <br><br> <a href="http://policies.ucf.edu/documents/3-401BombThreatorSuspiciousPackage.pdf" target="_blank">View pdf of full policy document</a></p> 
