        <div id="unit46-content"> 
         <div class="accordion_child"> 
          <p><br> POLICY STATEMENT:<br> The university establishes its investment parameters in accordance with sections 1011.42(5) and 218.415, Florida Statutes, and the UCF Investment Policy Manual. The vice president for administration and finance or designee will consolidate, where practicable and allowable, cash balances and investments from all funds covered by this policy to minimize risk exposure and maintain liquidity while maximizing investment earnings.<br><br> <a href="http://policies.ucf.edu/documents/3-113InvestmentsFINALonletterhead.pdf" target="_blank">View pdf of full policy document</a></p> 
